Entries.default: "You ready for an adventure? Cause I sure am!"
"Are we gonna fight someone? I want to throw the first punch!"
"When are we going to Ukaizo?"
"I don't like that hat you're wearing..."
"Thanks for letting me tag along. The Deadfire is awfully big for this little orlan."
"Can I borrow a sword? I promise to be careful."
"Why's everyone looking at me funny?"
"I know you told me to cover my eyes, but I'm not gonna."
"Maybe I should have stayed in Port Maje."
"Why is everything so expensive here?"
"Captain, my tummy hurts in a throwing-up way."
"Can we slow down and look at the pretty churches?"
"Neat place. I wonder if there's anyone to play with around here."
"Ow! Scraped my knee."
"I like how you're always smiling, mister Vatnir. You're a nice man."
"Um. Miss Fassina?"
"Konstanten, will you help me open this jar of hagfish?"
"Why do you wear skeptacles?"
"Hi."
"You return for more Seki lessons?"
"You talk funny. I like you. Can I brush your hair? Do you want to hear about my dreams?"
"Ku? Uhh... ta."
"Regardless, they bend light, focusing my vision of nearby objects. It helps me to read fine print."
"Can I try them on?"
"Absolu - you would get a headache, child."
"But I want to see things like you do! You're so nice and interesting."
"Then read more."
"I want to be just like you."
"Hi little bird! Hi! I like your feathers. Can we be friends?"
*squawk!*
"He talked! He talked to me!"
"Yes, yes, a pillar of charm. So everyone keeps telling me."
"If everyone smiled as much as you, the captain wouldn't have to work so hard on making people happy."
"Were I the Duskspeaker, I would throw anyone who complained into the sea. That would end the complaints, wouldn't it?"
"What is it, child? Did you break something?"
"It's not that. I know you don't like imps, or music, or jokes, or talking."
"But I think you're swell. And pretty. And you deserve to be happy."
"...Thank you, child. Agracima. I will take it under advisement. You are very small and very nice."
"Konstanten thinks so, too."
"No way, little miss. Looks expired. Where'd you get that, anywany?"
"You got me, mister. I stole it. You're not gonna tell anyone, are you?"
"That depends. You stop putting ants in my bedroll, and I'll think about it."
"In that case, can you help me unlock this pretty box? I... um, found it. In a drawer."
"Gods be damned, we gotta find you some real parents."
"I'm safe with you, captain. I just know it is all."
"Ripple sponge smells funny. Can I have some?"
"Want to see how many cinder bombs I can juggle? I've been practicing."
"Can I have another bite of that pie you're carrying? It was really good..."
"I'm learning a lot."
"I can't wait to make some new friends."
"I bit my tongue. Kinda hurts."
"Bam pituk, zidaka."
"Do we have to?"
"Lash kihun leza, Zivela?"
"K-ke hun yu leza!"
"You came from far away, didn't you? I came from far away too."
"'Spectacles,' Vela. Though skepticles might be a valuable contribution to society."
